---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import CTABand from '@/components/CTABand.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Life Insurance | Heidi Blondin Financial"
  description="Find the right life insurance coverage for your family. Term, whole life, and universal life options explained by an independent CFP® advisor in Kingston, Ontario."
>

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="bg-brand-plum py-20">
    <div class="container-content max-w-3xl">
      <p class="eyebrow-light mb-5">Insurance</p>
      <h1 class="font-serif text-display text-white text-balance" style="font-optical-sizing: auto;">Life Insurance: It's Peace of Mind</h1>
      <p class="font-sans text-[18px] text-white/65 mt-5 leading-relaxed">
        Whether you're safeguarding your family's future, protecting your hard-earned savings, or building long-term financial security, our tailored insurance solutions are designed to meet your unique needs. With trusted insurance providers, clear advice, and a caring approach, we make it easy for Canadians to make confident, informed decisions that protect what matters most.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why invest in life insurance -->
  <section class="bg-white section-gap">
    <div class="container-content max-w-3xl">
      <h2 class="font-serif text-h2 text-brand-plum mb-6" style="font-optical-sizing: auto;">Why You Should Invest in Life Insurance</h2>
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="border-l-2 border-brand-plum/20 pl-5 py-1">
          <h3 class="font-sans text-sm font-semibold text-brand-plum mb-1">Protect Your Loved Ones</h3>
          <p class="font-sans text-[15px] text-brand-ink/70 leading-relaxed">Life insurance provides financial security for your family or business if the unexpected happens—helping cover expenses, debts, and future needs. Especially important for the primary source of family income.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="border-l-2 border-brand-plum/20 pl-5 py-1">
          <h3 class="font-sans text-sm font-semibold text-brand-plum mb-1">Affordable Safety Net</h3>
          <p class="font-sans text-[15px] text-brand-ink/70 leading-relaxed">Protect your family during key life stages.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="border-l-2 border-brand-plum/20 pl-5 py-1">
          <h3 class="font-sans text-sm font-semibold text-brand-plum mb-1">Peace of Mind</h3>
          <p class="font-sans text-[15px] text-brand-ink/70 leading-relaxed">Rest easy knowing your loved ones are protected—today, tomorrow, and beyond.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="border-l-2 border-brand-plum/20 pl-5 py-1">
          <h3 class="font-sans text-sm font-semibold text-brand-plum mb-1">Build Wealth &amp; Leave a Legacy</h3>
          <p class="font-sans text-[15px] text-brand-ink/70 leading-relaxed">Grow your wealth tax efficiently and plan your legacy with a meaningful gift to the people and causes you care about.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-8">
        <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary inline-block">Request A Life Insurance Quote Online</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Term Life Insurance -->
  <section class="bg-brand-tintPlum section-gap">
    <div class="container-content max-w-3xl">
      <h2 class="font-serif text-h2 text-brand-plum mb-2" style="font-optical-sizing: auto;">Term Life Insurance</h2>
      <p class="font-sans text-[17px] text-brand-ink/70 italic mb-5">Affordable coverage for your working years.</p>
      <ul class="font-sans text-[15px] text-brand-ink/75 leading-relaxed space-y-2 mb-6 list-disc list-inside">
        <li>Low monthly cost for high coverage</li>
        <li>Choose 10, 20, or 30 year terms to match your needs</li>
        <li>Simple protection with flexible options to extend or convert later</li>
        <li>Great for families and professionals who want peace of mind without breaking the budget.</li>
      </ul>

      <!-- Expandable: Top Reasons to Buy Term Life Insurance -->
      <details class="border border-brand-plum/20 rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
        <summary class="cursor-pointer bg-white px-5 py-4 font-sans text-sm font-semibold text-brand-plum select-none">Top Reasons to Buy Term Life Insurance</summary>
        <div class="bg-white px-5 pb-5 pt-3 space-y-5">
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-sans text-sm font-semibold text-brand-plum mb-1">1. Affordable Protection During High-Responsibility Years</h4>
            <p class="font-sans text-[14px] text-brand-ink/70 leading-relaxed">Term life insurance offers high coverage at a low monthly cost, making it ideal for families, homeowners, and professionals during their prime working years. You can secure the protection you need without straining your budget.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-sans text-sm font-semibold text-brand-plum mb-1">2. Income Replacement &amp; Debt Coverage</h4>
            <p class="font-sans text-[14px] text-brand-ink/70 leading-relaxed">If the primary income earner passes away, term life insurance provides a tax-free lump sum to help surviving family members: Replace lost income / Pay off mortgages or loans / Cover final expenses like funerals and taxes. This is especially important given that a large portion of Canadian families are financially vulnerable and would face hardship quickly if they lost their primary income.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-sans text-sm font-semibold text-brand-plum mb-1">3. Customizable Terms</h4>
            <p class="font-sans text-[14px] text-brand-ink/70 leading-relaxed">You can choose coverage for 10, 20, or 30 years to match your financial obligations. Like raising children / paying off a mortgage / running a business</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-sans text-sm font-semibold text-brand-plum mb-1">4. Simplicity &amp; Flexibility</h4>
            <p class="font-sans text-[14px] text-brand-ink/70 leading-relaxed">Term life is easy to understand—no investment components, just pure protection. Many term insurance policies offer the ability to exchange to a longer term or convert to permanent coverage without a medical exam. Converting to permanent coverage allows you to create a legacy with lifetime protection.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-sans text-sm font-semibold text-brand-plum mb-1">5. Ideal for Canadians at Key Life Stages</h4>
            <ul class="font-sans text-[14px] text-brand-ink/70 leading-relaxed list-disc list-inside space-y-1 mt-1">
              <li>Young families protecting children's future</li>
              <li>Homeowners covering mortgage debt</li>
              <li>Business owners securing loans, key employees or succession plans</li>
              <li>Anyone with dependents who rely on their income</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </details>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Whole Life Insurance -->
  <section class="bg-white section-gap">
    <div class="container-content max-w-3xl">
      <h2 class="font-serif text-h2 text-brand-plum mb-2" style="font-optical-sizing: auto;">Whole Life Insurance</h2>
      <p class="font-sans text-[17px] text-brand-ink/70 italic mb-5">Lifetime protection with built-in savings.</p>
      <ul class="font-sans text-[15px] text-brand-ink/75 leading-relaxed space-y-2 mb-6 list-disc list-inside">
        <li>Coverage that never expires</li>
        <li>Builds cash value you can leverage or leave as a legacy</li>
        <li>Fixed premiums and long-term financial growth</li>
        <li>Ideal for estate planning, gifting, or creating a lasting legacy for loved ones.</li>
      </ul>

      <!-- Expandable: Top Reasons to Buy Whole Life Insurance -->
      <details class="border border-brand-plum/20 rounded-lg overflow-hidden mb-8">
        <summary class="cursor-pointer bg-brand-tintPlum px-5 py-4 font-sans text-sm font-semibold text-brand-plum select-none">Top Reasons to Buy Whole Life Insurance</summary>
        <div class="bg-brand-tintPlum px-5 pb-5 pt-3 space-y-5">
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-sans text-sm font-semibold text-brand-plum mb-1">1. Lifelong Coverage</h4>
            <p class="font-sans text-[14px] text-brand-ink/70 leading-relaxed">Whole life insurance provides guaranteed protection for your entire life, as long as premiums are paid. Unlike term life insurance, which expires after a set period, whole life ensures your loved ones receive a tax-free death benefit no matter when you pass away.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-sans text-sm font-semibold text-brand-plum mb-1">2. Cash Value Growth</h4>
            <p class="font-sans text-[14px] text-brand-ink/70 leading-relaxed">A portion of your premium builds cash value that grows tax-deferred over time. This can be: Borrowed against for emergencies, business opportunities, or retirement / Used to offset future premiums / Left untouched to increase the death benefit</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-sans text-sm font-semibold text-brand-plum mb-1">3. Fixed Premiums</h4>
            <p class="font-sans text-[14px] text-brand-ink/70 leading-relaxed">Whole life policies come with level premiums that never increase, making budgeting easier and more predictable over time. There is also an option to accelerate your premiums to a fix term (i.e. 10 or 20 years) to pay off the premiums during your working years.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-sans text-sm font-semibold text-brand-plum mb-1">4. Estate Planning &amp; Legacy Building</h4>
            <ul class="font-sans text-[14px] text-brand-ink/70 leading-relaxed list-disc list-inside space-y-1 mt-1">
              <li>Cover final expenses and estate taxes</li>
              <li>Ensure the family cottage stays with those who love it most</li>
              <li>Leave a financial legacy for children or grandchildren</li>
              <li>Support business succession by creating liquidity to help your business transition smoothly</li>
              <li>Leaving a meaningful gift to your favorite charity</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-sans text-sm font-semibold text-brand-plum mb-1">5. Dividends &amp; Participation</h4>
            <p class="font-sans text-[14px] text-brand-ink/70 leading-relaxed">Many Canadian insurers offer participating whole life policies, which may pay annual dividends. These can be: Taken as cash / Used to buy additional coverage / Applied to reduce premiums</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-sans text-sm font-semibold text-brand-plum mb-1">6. Tax Advantages</h4>
            <ul class="font-sans text-[14px] text-brand-ink/70 leading-relaxed list-disc list-inside space-y-1 mt-1">
              <li>Cash value growth is tax-deferred inside the policy</li>
              <li>Third party collateral loans are not taxable</li>
              <li>Death benefits are generally tax-free to beneficiaries</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </details>

      <!-- Whole Life closing copy -->
      <div class="bg-brand-tintPlum border-l-4 border-brand-plum/30 p-6 rounded-r-lg space-y-4">
        <h3 class="font-serif text-h3 text-brand-plum" style="font-optical-sizing: auto;">Whole Life Insurance: A Lifetime of Protection and Peace of Mind</h3>
        <p class="font-sans text-[15px] text-brand-ink/75 leading-relaxed">Whole life insurance is more than just coverage—it's a lifelong financial asset. With guaranteed protection that never expires, fixed premiums that stay the same, and a cash value that grows over time, whole life insurance offers stability you can count on. Whether you're planning your legacy, covering final expenses, or building a tax-advantaged savings cushion, this policy is designed to support your long-term goals. Whole life insurance is a gift that keeps on giving.</p>
        <p class="font-sans text-[15px] text-brand-ink/75 leading-relaxed">At Heidi Blondin Financial, we help you choose a plan that fits your life today and grows with you into tomorrow. Let's build a future that's secure, flexible, and full of possibility.</p>
        <p class="font-sans text-[15px] text-brand-ink/75 leading-relaxed">We would be happy to build a personalized whole life illustrations showing projected cash values and guaranteed death benefits to suit your personal goals. Request a quote today!</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Sample Pricing -->
  <section class="bg-brand-tintPlum section-gap">
    <div class="container-content max-w-4xl">
      <h2 class="font-serif text-h2 text-brand-plum mb-8" style="font-optical-sizing: auto;">Sample 10-year Life Insurance Pricing:</h2>

      <!-- Male table -->
      <h3 class="font-sans text-base font-semibold text-brand-plum mb-3">Male, 10-year Term Insurance - Non-Smoker</h3>
