            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>

      <!-- Pricing disclaimer -->
      <div class="bg-white border-l-2 border-brand-plum/20 p-4">
        <p class="font-sans text-xs text-brand-ink/55 leading-relaxed">The sample pricing charts provided on this website are for informational purposes only and are based on Term 10 life insurance rates as of September 16th, 2025. Please note that all pricing is subject to change without prior notice and may vary depending on individual underwriting and approval by the insurance provider. Final rates are determined based on age, health, lifestyle, and other underwriting criteria. This chart does not constitute an offer or guarantee of coverage.</p>
