  <!-- How It Works -->
  <section class="bg-white section-gap">
    <div class="container-content max-w-3xl">
      <h2 class="font-serif text-h2 text-brand-plum mb-8" style="font-optical-sizing: auto;">How It Works</h2>
      <ol class="space-y-4">
        <li class="flex gap-4">
          <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-brand-plum text-white font-sans text-sm font-semibold flex items-center justify-center">1</span>
          <p class="font-sans text-[16px] text-brand-ink/75 leading-relaxed pt-1">Fill out our quick inquiry form.</p>
        </li>
        <li class="flex gap-4">
          <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-brand-plum text-white font-sans text-sm font-semibold flex items-center justify-center">2</span>
          <p class="font-sans text-[16px] text-brand-ink/75 leading-relaxed pt-1">Connect with one of our Licensed Insurance Advisors who will clarify your needs and explore the various options available.</p>
        </li>
        <li class="flex gap-4">
          <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-brand-plum text-white font-sans text-sm font-semibold flex items-center justify-center">3</span>
          <p class="font-sans text-[16px] text-brand-ink/75 leading-relaxed pt-1">Review and select the right coverage option for your situation and submit an application with our guidance.</p>
        </li>
        <li class="flex gap-4">
          <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-brand-plum text-white font-sans text-sm font-semibold flex items-center justify-center">4</span>
          <p class="font-sans text-[16px] text-brand-ink/75 leading-relaxed pt-1">Accept your new policy and enjoy the peace of mind knowing your loved ones are protected.</p>
        </li>
      </ol>

      <div class="mt-8">
        <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary inline-block">Request A Life Insurance Quote Online</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Learn More About The Process -->
  <section class="bg-brand-tintPlum section-gap">
    <div class="container-content max-w-3xl">
      <h2 class="font-serif text-h2 text-brand-plum mb-3" style="font-optical-sizing: auto;">Learn More About The Process</h2>
      <p class="font-sans text-[17px] text-brand-ink/70 mb-8 leading-relaxed">We believe in keeping things simple, transparent, and efficient for you. Getting life insurance with us is straightforward:</p>

      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg">
          <h3 class="font-sans text-base font-semibold text-brand-plum mb-2">Personalized Needs Analysis</h3>
          <p class="font-sans text-[14px] text-brand-ink/70 leading-relaxed">Schedule a chat. We'll start with a friendly conversation (phone or Zoom, whatever works for you) to understand your situation and goals. One of our Insurance advisors will ask a few questions about your family, finances, and what you want the insurance to do (e.g., cover your mortgage, leave money for education, etc.). This helps us figure out how much coverage you actually need and what type fits best. Because we're brokers, we then research quotes from multiple insurers to find the best options for you (considering price and coverage features).</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg">
          <h3 class="font-sans text-base font-semibold text-brand-plum mb-2">Choose Your Plan &amp; Apply</h3>
          <p class="font-sans text-[14px] text-brand-ink/70 leading-relaxed">Review your options. Your Insurance advisor will present you with the top 1-3 insurance solutions that match your needs. They will explain the differences (cost, coverage highlights, any unique perks) so you can make an informed decision. Once you pick a plan you're comfortable with, we handle the application paperwork together. Your insurance advisor will help you fill out the application form (it's shorter than you might think) and coordinate any next steps like a medical questionnaire or arranging a quick paramedical exam, if required. Don't worry – many applications don't need an exam these days, and if they do, it's usually just a quick nurse visit for blood pressure and blood sample, paid for by the insurer. We make this step as convenient as possible, guiding you through every field and form.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg">
          <h3 class="font-sans text-base font-semibold text-brand-plum mb-2">Approval &amp; Policy Delivery</h3>
          <p class="font-sans text-[14px] text-brand-ink/70 leading-relaxed">Get covered. We submit your application to the insurance company (often electronically). Then we keep you updated as it moves through underwriting. If the insurer has any follow-up questions, we liaise and help you answer them. Once approved, we'll deliver your policy documents. Your Insurance advisor will walk you through the key details of your new policy so you fully understand it. And that's it – you can rest easy knowing you've secured the best solution available on the market, tailored just for you.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg">
          <h3 class="font-sans text-base font-semibold text-brand-plum mb-2">Ongoing Support</h3>
          <p class="font-sans text-[14px] text-brand-ink/70 leading-relaxed">Our relationship doesn't end at delivery. We're here for you over the years to come. Need to update a beneficiary? Have questions about your coverage? Want to review if your coverage amount is still adequate? Just reach out – we provide ongoing customer support. And when the time comes (hopefully far in the future) that your family needs to file a claim, we'll be there to assist and make sure it's handled smoothly.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-8 bg-white border-l-4 border-brand-plum/30 p-6 rounded-r-lg">
        <h3 class="font-sans text-base font-semibold text-brand-plum mb-2">No Stress, No Hassle – Guaranteed</h3>
        <p class="font-sans text-[14px] text-brand-ink/70 leading-relaxed">From start to finish, we aim to make buying life insurance refreshingly easy. We know your time is valuable, so we do the heavy lifting. Our clients often tell us they're surprised by how quick and painless the process is compared to what they expected. We take care of the details so you can focus on what matters: enjoying life knowing your loved ones are protected.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why Work With Us -->
  <section class="bg-white section-gap">
    <div class="container-content max-w-3xl">
      <h2 class="font-serif text-h2 text-brand-plum mb-8" style="font-optical-sizing: auto;">Why work with us?</h2>
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="border-l-2 border-brand-plum/20 pl-5 py-1">
          <h3 class="font-sans text-sm font-semibold text-brand-plum mb-1">Independent &amp; Unbiased</h3>
          <p class="font-sans text-[15px] text-brand-ink/70 leading-relaxed">As independent brokers, we shop from numerous top insurers to find you the best coverage at the best price. We are not tied to one company – our only goal is to secure you the right policy.</p>
        </div>
